{"body": "Single-quoted strings are NOT VALID JSON. See section 2.5 here: http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc4627.txt\r\n\r\nFor that matter, single-quoted values as keys (ie, `'foo'` in `{'foo': 'bar'}`) aren't even valid *Javascript*.\r\n\r\nShort story shorter: if you're producing \"JSON\" with single quotes, you are wrong. If somebody is sending you \"JSON\" with single quotes, THEY are wrong. Error out and tell them to fix their broken code.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/15028552", "created_at": "2013-03-17T19:05:43Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9188#issuecomment-15028552", "updated_at": "2013-03-17T19:05:43Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 9188, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/al2o3cr", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6883e5ef03484d4fcef507d7b4f1d243?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fb20bb95ab626d93fd976af958fbc61ba.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6883e5ef03484d4fcef507d7b4f1d243", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "al2o3cr", "type": "User", "id": 1191, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ec51bd3543c151009cb6"}, "id": 15028552, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9188"}
